Description: Measured in years for each individual.
Takes the value of 1 if individual is female and 0 if male.
Takes the value of 1 if individual graduated from High School or College and 0  otherwise.
Takes the value of 1 if individual graduated with a Master's degree and 0  otherwise.
Takes the value of 1 if individual graduated with a Bachelor's degree and 0  otherwise.
Takes the value of 1 if individual works in government sector job and 0 otherwise.
Takes the value of 1 if individual works in private for profit sector and 0 otherwise.
Takes the value of 1 if individual works in private for non-profit sector and 0 otherwise.
Takes the value 1 if individual is white and 0 if he/she is black.
